<b style="font-size: larger;">History :</b><br>&nbsp; 
The group derives its origins from textile retailing and wholesaling and has an experience of over 100 years in the trade. Avika branched out into the field of Jewellery retailing in the year 1993 &nbsp; by opening its first store in Udaipur. 
The reason behind the Avika group's into business itself is quite unique and makes it interesting to read. The ancestors of the current management come from a previous background that comprised of priests, saints and advisors to kings. Hailing from the Udaipur district of Rajasthan.<br><br>&nbsp;


